{"tid":2301673,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"連登會員：反全球化#225931 表示 中大計算機科學學科表現驕人","createTime":"2020-11-26T13:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T23:43:27.000Z","uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62ac2d60f0094e62f182593a1bddd56c3cd8d296","tid":2301673,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"【中大計算機科學學科表現驕人💻💫】<br />\n世界大學排名權威之一《美國新聞與世界報道》雜誌最新公布的2021年「全球最佳大學學科排名」，中大計算機科學學科勇奪佳績，位列香港第一及全球第十一位。<br />\n中大工程學院院長黃定發教授表示: 「這足證中大的研究實力和影響力能與世界頂尖大學並列，廣受國際認同。工程學院能在教學和研究方面具備卓越表現，實有賴教研團隊的共同努力和付出。在推動科研發展路上，我們會堅持不懈，並全力培育更多優秀人才，保持學院的頂級學術水平。」了解詳情：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2V4d2Qc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2V4d2Qc&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=4ceeeb69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2V4d2Qc</a> <br />\n#博文約禮中大人 #全球最佳大學學科排名 #中大計算機科學 #中大工程學院"},{"pid":"f5ed2dcb614da26bf9ba9706d5de5ba2b4e1e0fe","tid":2301673,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2241cac5e1c5292b4d83221150088ac1e3e2812","tid":2301673,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:32:41.000Z","msg":"香港第一？認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bba87a707f49c3f027226deb238b40b042da31","tid":2301673,"uid":143167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T19:00:12.000Z","msg":"排名會依據研究文獻的發表數量、研究書籍出版量、被引述次數、全球及地區的學術聲譽及國際合作（International collaboration）等指標去釐定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756efd9e7775d9971374d5a8faccf1ec0f04d471","tid":2301673,"uid":8051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2241cac5e1c5292b4d83221150088ac1e3e2812","tid":2301673,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply